Detailed Description

The class represents IPDR VERSION_REQUEST message. The message has the following structure: <xmp> struct VersionRequest { int requesterAddress; // IPv4 address of the version request initiator int requesterBootTime; // boot time of the version request initiator (in seconds from epoch time) char [4] msg; // MUST be 'CRAN' for version 1 and 'IPDR' for version 2 } </xmp>
